translate french baimovietheaterstartdate_13ddb197:

    # "We get to the theater and find seats in the back."
    "On arrive au cinéma et on trouve des places au fond."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baimoviedate.rpy:26
translate french baimovietheaterstartdate_7b36967b:

    # "We chat for a while before the movie starts."
    "On discute un moment avant que le film commence."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baimoviedate.rpy:31
translate french baimovietheaterstartdate_592835a4:

    # "Finally the movie starts up and we go silent."
    "Enfin, le film démarre et on se tait."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baimoviedate.rpy:33
translate french baimovietheaterstartdate_aee76b2d:

    # "The trailers take up about fifteen minutes, then the movie really gets started."
    "Les bandes-annonces durent environ quinze minutes, puis le film commence vraiment."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baimoviedate.rpy:35
translate french baimovietheaterstartdate_5e17c29c:

    # "It's a pretty good movie and we laugh all the way through it."
    "C'est un film plutôt sympa et on rigole tout du long."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baimoviedate.rpy:37
translate french baimovietheaterstartdate_a2905b6a:

    # "After the movie ends, we hang out and chat through the credits."
    "Une fois le film terminé, on traîne et on discute pendant le générique."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiDates/baimoviedate.rpy:42
translate french baimovietheaterstartdate_edff30b2:

    # "When the credits end, we walk outside together to my car."
    "Quand le générique se termine, on sort ensemble pour rejoindre ma voiture."

